caption: I've been wanting to meet these 2 guys for the longest time, and I finally did. The exact day of this picture actually. They mean so much to me, and they've helped me through their songs and it would just mean so much to just get another hug from them and tell them how much they mean to me and how much they mean to other people and to reunite with them would mean the world to me! I recently just won tickets to meet Little Mix, so I was joking around with my friend saying "maybe if I still have my luck, I can meet jack and jack again" and maybe that will happen! Idk!! Looking forward to whoever wins! Good luck everyone❤️❤️ #contest @jackandjackofficial @jackjohnsonofficial @jackgilinskyofficial
